short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get test results and status of Jenkins test builds

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension pulls the test results of your specific job builds and shows the pass/fail status. It also shows the total. pass and fail count of tests that ran in that build.
